On  at , Krzysiek Jonko tippy-tappy-typed:

> I'm trying to use OpenWindowtaglist instead of standard OpenWindow
> command (look inside my little example) But I've a lot of problems:
> 1. how can I get IDCMP messages from opened window?
> 2. how can I print texts in this window (some kind of WindowOutput)?
> 3. how can I attach standard or GadTools gadgets?
> 
