There /are/ limits. You could try to have a smaller display. There is
quite a lot of blitter time difference between a 256 and a 200 height
screen.

What CPU do you have? You could try a cpu-based blit routine perhaps.

> 3) I still need a crossfade routine for 2 256 colors pics. For example:
